I'm afraid to hear.

655
00:34:34,682 --> 00:34:37,015
It's the word
you're going to use.

656
00:34:37,096 --> 00:34:39,911
Love. Last week I didn't know
what it meant.

657
00:34:39,992 --> 00:34:42,325
Then I checked in
to the Plaza Hotel.

658
00:34:42,406 --> 00:34:43,854
Know what happened there?

659
00:34:43,934 --> 00:34:45,745
