in this building.

683
00:35:50,235 --> 00:35:51,161
Like who?

684
00:35:51,201 --> 00:35:53,092
In Apartment 1C
are the Boscos,

685
00:35:53,132 --> 00:35:54,540
Mr. And Mrs.
J. Bosco.

686
00:35:54,580 --> 00:35:55,988
Who are they?

687
00:35:56,028 --> 00:35:58,402
A lovely young couple
of the same sex.

688
00:35:58,442 --> 00:36:00,816
No one knows
which one that is.

689
00:36:00,856 --> 00:36:03,230
In 3C are
Mr. And Mrs. Gonzales...

690
00:36:03,270 --> 00:36:05,644
Mr. And Mrs. Armandariz,
and Mr. Calhoun,

691
00:36:05,685 --> 00:36:07,575
who must be
the umpire.

692
00:36:07,616 --> 00:36:09,506
Guess who lives in 4D.

693
00:36:09,547 --> 00:36:10,954
I don't know.

694
00:36:10,995 --> 00:36:12,322
Nobody else does either.

695
00:36:12,402 --> 00:36:14,253
Nobody's been seen
in three years,

696
00:36:14,334 --> 00:36:17,029
