with a can opener.

699
00:36:21,455 --> 00:36:23,789
Victor Velasco
lives in 6A, the attic.

700
00:36:23,829 --> 00:36:26,202
He's 58. He skis,
he climbs mountains,

701
00:36:26,282 --> 00:36:28,134
